The Laws of Zambia
"transfer" includes convey, assign, surrender or otherwise alienate or dispose of
land or other property, and "transfer" as a noun shall be correspondingly
construed;
"urban area" means the area of a city, municipality or township as defined in the Cap. 281
Local Government Act.
PART II
COMPULSORY ACQUISITION
